body.name: FATORRI Coffee Table for Living Room, Rustic Wood Center Table with Shelves, Farmhouse Rectangle Cocktail Tea Tables (Rustic Oak)
features: [Wood Coffee Tables for Living Room]: Whether serving as a center table in the living room or providing a perch for a mug of coffee, this wood coffee table is sure to be a stylish stage. It features two cubes and a central adjustable shelf, providing a perfect place to lay out coasters, books, a remote control, or snacks. It also comes with adjustable levelers, ensuring that it does not wobble once set up.

[Rustic Oak Wood Finish]: Defined by clean lines and a neutral finish, this wood coffee table puts a farmhouse twist on a fashion design. The open metal frame gives this piece an airy feel, while the wood top showcases a rectangular silhouette that’s ideal for holding living room essentials. Keep daily necessities close at hand while adding a touch of industrial flair to your living room.

[High Weight Capacity]: Thanks to the high-grade material and well-structured design, this rustic coffee table stands very stable. The 1-inch chunky tabletop and 2 support legs under the bottom shelf significantly increase its weight capacity. This coffee table has a weight capacity of 300 lbs for both the tabletop and the bottom shelf.
[Dimensions & Durable Materials]: The overall size is D 20.86” x W 43.31”x H 18.50”. Crafted from high-grade MDF and long-lasting heavy-duty metal, this coffee table is perfect for small spaces.

[Super Easy to Assemble]: It takes around 30 minutes to assemble this farmhouse coffee table. We also provide clear instructions and all the necessary tools. If you have any questions before or after purchasing, you can email us anytime, and we will reply within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very easy to put together and feels very solid! Love the storage and the overall look is great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty & Easy to Assemble
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful look and very easy to assemble. Great, durable quality too. Wood is lighter in color than pictures featured, but I liked the light color even better.I would recommend to all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solidly built coffee table at a great price
reviews.reviewText: The coffee table is well built and easy to put together. The top and lower shelf are sturdy solid wood, and the side and supports are solid metal. It took no more than 15 minutes to put together and it is very stable and sturdy. It’s a great table at a great price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This coffee table looks great in our new apartment. We were trying to match different wood finishes in our apartment that it came with, and this rustic oak color looks so nice with other wood tones in the same room! My husband works in sheet metal and loves putting furniture and things together. He said the hardware is a little difficult to work with (a little cheap). When all things were said and done, the coffee table looks great in our living room and is sturdy enough to put our feet up on it if we wanted to. There is no wobbling or shaking once it is put together completely!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The pieces were well marked and went together easily. The table is a nice addition to our TV room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together and looks better then I thought

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars For the price, this is great.
reviews.reviewText: I needed a coffee table asap, so after browsing Amazon for a bit I decided on this one because it looked like it could be nice, it was inexpensive, and would be delivered the next day. It did not disappoint. I put it together by myself in less than 20 mins. It seems pretty sturdy and the color is nice, not too dark and not too light. Not sure how well the table top will hold up, but for the price I’m not complaining.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy instructions, beautiful craftsmanship, wonderful customer service
reviews.reviewText: We bought the coffee table and the entertainment stand from Fatorri and we love both. The materials are sturdy and feel like good quality, it it feels more heavy duty than ikea or comparable other brands on Amazon (we also bought vecelo night stands and end tables at the same time).The instructions were much easier to follow than Vecelo or ikea ones. The edges of the wood and the metal welded edges were smoother than both of those brands, too.We did have a concern with the coffee table being damaged during shipping, however the Fatorri customer service was super helpful and responded within a few hours. Amazon required us to return the item, which would have been a pain in the butt because of how big it is, but Fatorri customer service actually provided 2 different options to solve the concern.I’m sold on this brand for sure! I just wish they also made end tables to match the dark wood colors (but if you’re looking, the dark wood from Fatorri matches the “gray” wood from vecelo fairly nicely). Also, I love that these black baskets fit so perfectly in the center and side cubbies (also on Amazon!)
